            "width": 524,
            "height": 400,
            "content": "## Guesty Booking → Guest SMS Lifecycle\n\n**How it works:**\n1. Receives new reservation from Guesty webhook\n2. Normalizes guest data + check-in/out dates, listing, confirmation code\n3. Creates guest contact in Aloware with reservation details\n4. Sends instant booking confirmation SMS\n5. Enrolls in Check-in Reminder Sequence (3-day, 1-day, day-of)\n6. Waits until 18 hours after checkout\n7. Enrolls in Post-Stay Review Request Sequence\n\n**Setup:**\n- Set n8n Variables: `ALOWARE_API_TOKEN`, `ALOWARE_LINE_PHONE`, `ALOWARE_CHECKIN_SEQUENCE_ID`, `ALOWARE_REVIEW_SEQUENCE_ID`, `PROPERTY_COMPANY_NAME`\n- In Guesty, create webhook for \"New Reservation\" events\n- Create 2 Aloware Sequences (Check-in Reminders + Post-Stay Review)"
